title: Lady Gaga - Discography [320kbps]
description:
Presenting the Lady Gaga Discography... For more information on Lady Gaga go to: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lady_Gaga

I have put the discography together for her, these are the main albums and all that is important. She has only really done 3 albums since she started and also an EP. This is all you need really. They are MP3s, I have sourced them all from lossless quality to make sure they sound as perfect as possible.

All the tags have been done, the front covers are included. Sorry I couldn't get the right back covers it is a bit confusing and they don't seem to be available. The MP3s are at 320kbps/44.1Khz quality.

Please help to seed this well, I know there's probably some other discographies of Gaga but this one I have made in my own style like my other discographies. I hope you enjoy these tracks. Thanks for downloading!

Releases included as follows:

(2008) Lady Gaga - The Fame
(2009) Lady Gaga - The Fame Monster [EP]
(2011) Lady Gaga - Born This Way
(2013) Lady Gaga - ARTPOP
